articles.title: #8 Toyota demoted for exceeding power limit in WEC Monza race - Motorsport.com
articles.description: A 50-second penalty handed down to the World Endurance Championship points-leading #8 Toyota in the 6 Hours of Monza has demoted it from fourth to sixth in the final results.
